document_data.mainbody:
Keltarn Street was a small road that was located in the city of Waterdeep.
Keltarn Street was located in the northern section of Waterdeeps Castle Ward. It ran east to west just south of Siren Lane, connecting the much larger Street of Silver to the east with Swords Street to the west. Keltarn Street also intersected the Street of Silks near its midpoint.
